{"_default": {"1": {"id": "JER.22", "bibleId": "f72b840c855f362c-04", "number": "22", "bookId": "JER", "reference": "Jeremiah 22", "copyright": "\n          \n            PUBLIC DOMAIN\n          \n        ", "content": [{"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "p"}, "items": [{"text": "The LORD said, \u201cGo down to the house of the king of Judah, and speak this word there: ", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.1", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.1"]}}, {"text": "\u2018Hear the LORD\u2019s word, king of Judah, who sits on David\u2019s throne\u2014you, your servants, and your people who enter in by these gates. ", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.2", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.2"]}}, {"text": "The LORD says: \u201cExecute justice and righteousness, and deliver him who is robbed out of the hand of the oppressor. Do no wrong. Do no violence to the foreigner, the fatherless, or the widow. Don\u2019t shed innocent blood in this place. ", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.3", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.3"]}}, {"text": "For if you do this thing indeed, then kings sitting on David\u2019s throne will enter in by the gates of this house, riding in chariots and on horses\u2014they, their servants, and their people. ", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.4", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.4"]}}, {"text": "But if you will not hear these words, I swear by myself,\u201d says the LORD, \u201cthat this house will become a desolation.\u201d\u2019\u201d", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.5", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.5"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "p"}, "items": [{"text": "For the LORD says concerning the house of the king of Judah:", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.6", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.6"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1", "vid": "JER 22:6"}, "items": [{"text": "\u201cYou are Gilead to me,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.6", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.6"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:6"}, "items": [{"text": "the head of Lebanon.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.6", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.6"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1", "vid": "JER 22:6"}, "items": [{"text": "Yet surely I will make you a wilderness,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.6", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.6"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:6"}, "items": [{"text": "cities which are not inhabited.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.6", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.6"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "I will prepare destroyers against you,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.7", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.7"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:7"}, "items": [{"text": "everyone with his weapons,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.7", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.7"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1", "vid": "JER 22:7"}, "items": [{"text": "and they will cut down your choice cedars,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.7", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.7"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:7"}, "items": [{"text": "and cast them into the fire.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.7", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.7"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "p"}, "items": [{"text": "\u201cMany nations will pass by this city, and they will each ask his neighbor, \u2018Why has the LORD done this to this great city?\u2019 ", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.8", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.8"]}}, {"text": "Then they will answer, \u2018Because they abandoned the covenant of the LORD their God, worshiped other gods, and served them.\u2019\u201d", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.9", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.9"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "Don\u2019t weep for the dead.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.10", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.10"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:10"}, "items": [{"text": "Don\u2019t bemoan him;", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.10", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.10"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1", "vid": "JER 22:10"}, "items": [{"text": "but weep bitterly for him who goes away,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.10", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.10"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:10"}, "items": [{"text": "for he will return no more,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.10", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.10"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:10"}, "items": [{"text": "and not see his native country.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.10", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.10"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "m"}, "items": [{"text": "For the LORD says touching Shallum the son of Josiah, king of Judah, who reigned instead of Josiah his father, and who went out of this place: \u201cHe won\u2019t return there any more. ", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.11", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.11"]}}, {"text": "But he will die in the place where they have led him captive. He will see this land no more.\u201d", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.12", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.12"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "\u201cWoe to him who builds his house by unrighteousness,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.13", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.13"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:13"}, "items": [{"text": "and his rooms by injustice;", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.13", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.13"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1", "vid": "JER 22:13"}, "items": [{"text": "who uses his neighbor\u2019s service without wages,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.13", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.13"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:13"}, "items": [{"text": "and doesn\u2019t give him his hire;", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.13", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.13"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "who says, \u2018I will build myself a wide house and spacious rooms,\u2019", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.14", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.14"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:14"}, "items": [{"text": "and cuts out windows for himself,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.14", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.14"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1", "vid": "JER 22:14"}, "items": [{"text": "with a cedar ceiling,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.14", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.14"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:14"}, "items": [{"text": "and painted with red.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.14", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.14"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "b"}, "items": []}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "\u201cShould you reign because you strive to excel in cedar?", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.15", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.15"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:15"}, "items": [{"text": "Didn\u2019t your father eat and drink,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.15", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.15"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:15"}, "items": [{"text": "and do justice and righteousness?", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.15", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.15"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:15"}, "items": [{"text": "Then it was well with him.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.15", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.15"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "He judged the cause of the poor and needy;", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.16", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.16"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:16"}, "items": [{"text": "so then it was well.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.16", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.16"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1", "vid": "JER 22:16"}, "items": [{"text": "Wasn\u2019t this to know me?\u201d", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.16", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.16"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:16"}, "items": [{"text": "says the LORD.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.16", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.16"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "But your eyes and your heart are only for your covetousness,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.17", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.17"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:17"}, "items": [{"text": "for shedding innocent blood,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.17", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.17"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:17"}, "items": [{"text": "for oppression, and for doing violence.\u201d", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.17", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.17"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "m"}, "items": [{"text": "Therefore the LORD says concerning Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah:", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.18", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.18"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1", "vid": "JER 22:18"}, "items": [{"text": "\u201cThey won\u2019t lament for him,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.18", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.18"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:18"}, "items": [{"text": "saying, \u2018Ah my brother!\u2019 or, \u2018Ah sister!\u2019", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.18", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.18"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1", "vid": "JER 22:18"}, "items": [{"text": "They won\u2019t lament for him,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.18", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.18"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:18"}, "items": [{"text": "saying \u2018Ah lord!\u2019 or, \u2018Ah his glory!\u2019", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.18", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.18"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "He will be buried with the burial of a donkey,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.19", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.19"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:19"}, "items": [{"text": "drawn and cast out beyond the gates of Jerusalem.\u201d", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.19", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.19"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "b"}, "items": []}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "\u201cGo up to Lebanon, and cry out.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.20", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.20"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:20"}, "items": [{"text": "Lift up your voice in Bashan,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.20", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.20"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1", "vid": "JER 22:20"}, "items": [{"text": "and cry from Abarim;", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.20", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.20"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:20"}, "items": [{"text": "for all your lovers have been destroyed.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.20", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.20"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "I spoke to you in your prosperity,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.21", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.21"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:21"}, "items": [{"text": "but you said, \u2018I will not listen.\u2019", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.21", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.21"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1", "vid": "JER 22:21"}, "items": [{"text": "This has been your way from your youth,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.21", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.21"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:21"}, "items": [{"text": "that you didn\u2019t obey my voice.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.21", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.21"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "The wind will feed all your shepherds,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.22", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.22"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:22"}, "items": [{"text": "and your lovers will go into captivity.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.22", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.22"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1", "vid": "JER 22:22"}, "items": [{"text": "Surely then you will be ashamed", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.22", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.22"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:22"}, "items": [{"text": "and confounded for all your wickedness.", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.22", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.22"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "Inhabitant of Lebanon,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.23", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.23"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:23"}, "items": [{"text": "who makes your nest in the cedars,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.23", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.23"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1", "vid": "JER 22:23"}, "items": [{"text": "how greatly to be pitied you will be when pangs come on you,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.23", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.23"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:23"}, "items": [{"text": "the pain as of a woman in travail!", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.23", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.23"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "p"}, "items": [{"text": "\u201cAs I live,\u201d says the LORD, \u201cthough Coniah the son of Jehoiakim king of Judah were the signet on my right hand, I would still pluck you from there. ", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.24", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.24"]}}, {"text": "I would give you into the hand of those who seek your life, and into the hand of them of whom you are afraid, even into the hand of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, and into the hand of the Kasdim. ", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.25", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.25"]}}, {"text": "I will cast you out with your mother who bore you into another country, where you were not born; and there you will die. ", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.26", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.26"]}}, {"text": "But to the land to which their soul longs to return, there they will not return.\u201d", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.27", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.27"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "Is this man Coniah a despised broken vessel?", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.28", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.28"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:28"}, "items": [{"text": "Is he a vessel in which no one delights?", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.28", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.28"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1", "vid": "JER 22:28"}, "items": [{"text": "Why are they cast out, he and his offspring,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.28", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.28"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:28"}, "items": [{"text": "and cast into a land which they don\u2019t know?", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.28", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.28"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "O earth, earth, earth,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.29", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.29"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:29"}, "items": [{"text": "hear the LORD\u2019s word!", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.29", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.29"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1"}, "items": [{"text": "The LORD says,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.30", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.30"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:30"}, "items": [{"text": "\u201cRecord this man as childless,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.30", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.30"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:30"}, "items": [{"text": "a man who will not prosper in his days;", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.30", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.30"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q1", "vid": "JER 22:30"}, "items": [{"text": "for no more will a man of his offspring prosper,", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.30", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.30"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:30"}, "items": [{"text": "sitting on David\u2019s throne", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.30", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.30"]}}]}, {"name": "para", "type": "tag", "attrs": {"style": "q2", "vid": "JER 22:30"}, "items": [{"text": "and ruling in Judah.\u201d", "type": "text", "attrs": {"verseId": "JER.22.30", "verseOrgIds": ["JER.22.30"]}}]}], "next": {"id": "JER.23", "number": "23", "bookId": "JER"}, "previous": {"id": "JER.21", "number": "21", "bookId": "JER"}}}}